@scene tavern_merchant
title: A Merchant Arrives
is-card: true
tags: tavern_event
on-arrival: silver = silver + 1

A trader from the south enters, stamping snow from his boots. He overpays you for directions to the Jarl's hall.

Tagged with `tavern_event` — automatically included in the tag-based deck.

Silver: **[+ silver +]**

- @tag_demo_hand: Return to hand

@scene tavern_rumour
title: A Whispered Rumour
is-card: true
tags: tavern_event
on-arrival: reputation = reputation + 1

A huscarl leans close and tells you something useful about the Jarl's court. Whether it's true or not, knowing it makes you seem well-connected.

Tagged with `tavern_event` — automatically included.

Reputation: **[+ reputation +]**

